title: Eel Whole
description: Exotic, perhaps. Unique, for sure. Rich and succulent flavor of eel that is mildly sweet with a hint of earthiness. Deep frying makes crisp and crunchy, poaching yields softer texture, grilled is tender with satisfying chew.

title: Tuscan Branzino Whole
description: A Citarella Exclusive! Enjoy on your plate in less than 24 hours after it leaves the water! Tender, flaky meat that is mild, sweet, and juicy.

title: Arctic Char Whole
description: Native to the icy, northernmost waters of North America and Europe, arctic char is robust, rich red to ros√© pink fleshed fish. Norway-sourced, sustainably farmed, perfect for smoking Scandinavian-style. Kosher-friendly.
